\par\par
{\f1\fs22 1.  Pipeline Architecture Overview\line 2.  Stage 0: Auphonic Audio Cleanup\line 3.  Stage 1: OpenAI Whisper Speech-to-Text\line 4.  Stage 2: AssemblyAI Diarization\line 5.  Stage 3: Segment Merging & Post-Processing\line 6.  Stage 4: Claude Opus 4 Speaker Refinement\line 7.  Database Persistence & Checkpointing\line 8.  Error Handling & Recovery Architecture\line 9.  Known Issues & Risk Assessment\line 10. Recent Fixes (Pending Deployment)}
